  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Pastor's Lake - immerse yourself in the atmosphere of a summer cottage village.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Having inherited a house in the village, the hero finds himself in a quiet area, far from noisy cities, where you can have a good rest for your soul and heart, but, unfortunately, it is very abandoned.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Minimalist interface with only basic hints; everything else is discovered through personal experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Daynight cycle, with random precipitation causing mushrooms to regrow.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Needs System that can be replenished by either taking odd jobs or living entirely by gathering, fishing, or gardening. Groceries can also be purchased at the local store.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Various vehicles, from an ATV available at the beginning of the game to cars acquired as the game progresses. All personal vehicles consume fuel, which must be refueled at gas stations. One special car requires an oil change and can also be used as a taxi.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mission tasks for helping volunteers restore the local church and finding the town and its museum.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The ability to build a sauna in your yard, use it yourself, or rent it out.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The player can choose something he likes:  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Explore forest and village</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714920/extras/287fa57e781fd9908b496495854b8bf8.avif?t=1771435166\" width=1600 height=900 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Plough, sow and reap the harvest in the fields</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714920/extras/e32ba12b9e0af19b2ebe67c5365c79a9.poster.avif?t=1771435166\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714920/extras/e32ba12b9e0af19b2ebe67c5365c79a9.webm?t=1771435166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714920/extras/e32ba12b9e0af19b2ebe67c5365c79a9.mp4?t=1771435166\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714920/extras/abb676a608a3e6fa7499fe56db760f44.poster.avif?t=1771435166\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714920/extras/abb676a608a3e6fa7499fe56db760f44.webm?t=1771435166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714920/extras/abb676a608a3e6fa7499fe56db760f44.mp4?t=1771435166\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Pick, cook or sell mushrooms</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714920/extras/170f629504e4a4e309d2d0b3b162b90c.avif?t=1771435166\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714920/extras_big/170f629504e4a4e309d2d0b3b162b90c.avif?t=1771435166 width=1600 height=900 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714920/extras/70ef3b385375217f0f572fb9cd5d2e7b.poster.avif?t=1771435166\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714920/extras/70ef3b385375217f0f572fb9cd5d2e7b.webm?t=1771435166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714920/extras/70ef3b385375217f0f572fb9cd5d2e7b.mp4?t=1771435166\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Fishing</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714920/extras/2ad563a4674f22e3478f5611dba2c5da.poster.avif?t=1771435166\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714920/extras/2ad563a4674f22e3478f5611dba2c5da.webm?t=1771435166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714920/extras/2ad563a4674f22e3478f5611dba2c5da.mp4?t=1771435166\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Complete missions to build sauna </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714920/extras/e14a703cfc046f0368851f10632e2926.poster.avif?t=1771435166\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714920/extras/e14a703cfc046f0368851f10632e2926.webm?t=1771435166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714920/extras/e14a703cfc046f0368851f10632e2926.mp4?t=1771435166\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Complete various tasks to unlock items</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714920/extras/1dc7b048c07ce9c20571e0b21374b6c4.avif?t=1771435166\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714920/extras_big/1dc7b048c07ce9c20571e0b21374b6c4.avif?t=1771435166 width=800 height=450 /></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Get behind the wheel of various vehicles: from ATVs to old Soviet trucks</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714920/extras/903f3f3daa5e613305940b5b2e44c089.avif?t=1771435166\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714920/extras_big/903f3f3daa5e613305940b5b2e44c089.avif?t=1771435166 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Build a secluded summer-house with a sauna on an island in the middle of Pastor's Lake</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714920/extras/662d0dba4672403e5f2bba657f072888.avif?t=1771435166\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714920/extras_big/662d0dba4672403e5f2bba657f072888.avif?t=1771435166 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><u>Early Access Roadmap</u></strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_strike\"><i>Fishing with the option to sell or cook your catch</i></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_strike\"><i>Story-based quest about church restoration</i></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_strike\"><i>Sowing, harvesting, and selling wheat</i></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_strike\"><i>Transportation work - taxi, bus driver</i></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_strike\"><i>Leaderboards for game points, fish size, and crayfish catch</i></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_strike\"><i>Urban location (city Sosnovy Bor)</i></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_strike\"><i>Growing and harvesting tomatoes in the garden, maintaining a chicken coop</i></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_strike\"><i>Harvesting and bottling honey from the hive into containers</i></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_strike\">Hunting game with firearms and then selling the catch</span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tasks to restore everyday life in local villages, with an increasing number of NPCs as you progress</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crafting household items, food, and accessories</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customization of country house decor</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expanded quests for finding valuable items on the map</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expansion of the urban location with the introduction of new quests for earning in-game currency</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reworking the visual style of existing locations with an increase in Detailing</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Final fixes and improvements (to locations and game mechanics) before release</u></strong></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Pastor's Lake - immerse yourself in the atmosphere of a summer cottage village.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Having inherited a house in the village, the hero finds himself in a quiet area, far from noisy cities, where you can have a good rest for your soul and heart, but, unfortunately, it is very abandoned.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Minimalist interface with only basic hints; everything else is discovered through personal experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Daynight cycle, with random precipitation causing mushrooms to regrow.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Needs System that can be replenished by either taking odd jobs or living entirely by gathering, fishing, or gardening. Groceries can also be purchased at the local store.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Various vehicles, from an ATV available at the beginning of the game to cars acquired as the game progresses. All personal vehicles consume fuel, which must be refueled at gas stations. One special car requires an oil change and can also be used as a taxi.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mission tasks for helping volunteers restore the local church and finding the town and its museum.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The ability to build a sauna in your yard, use it yourself, or rent it out.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The player can choose something he likes:  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Explore forest and village</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714920/extras/287fa57e781fd9908b496495854b8bf8.avif?t=1771435166\" width=1600 height=900 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Plough, sow and reap the harvest in the fields</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714920/extras/e32ba12b9e0af19b2ebe67c5365c79a9.poster.avif?t=1771435166\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714920/extras/e32ba12b9e0af19b2ebe67c5365c79a9.webm?t=1771435166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714920/extras/e32ba12b9e0af19b2ebe67c5365c79a9.mp4?t=1771435166\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714920/extras/abb676a608a3e6fa7499fe56db760f44.poster.avif?t=1771435166\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714920/extras/abb676a608a3e6fa7499fe56db760f44.webm?t=1771435166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714920/extras/abb676a608a3e6fa7499fe56db760f44.mp4?t=1771435166\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Pick, cook or sell mushrooms</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714920/extras/170f629504e4a4e309d2d0b3b162b90c.avif?t=1771435166\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714920/extras_big/170f629504e4a4e309d2d0b3b162b90c.avif?t=1771435166 width=1600 height=900 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714920/extras/70ef3b385375217f0f572fb9cd5d2e7b.poster.avif?t=1771435166\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714920/extras/70ef3b385375217f0f572fb9cd5d2e7b.webm?t=1771435166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714920/extras/70ef3b385375217f0f572fb9cd5d2e7b.mp4?t=1771435166\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Fishing</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714920/extras/2ad563a4674f22e3478f5611dba2c5da.poster.avif?t=1771435166\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714920/extras/2ad563a4674f22e3478f5611dba2c5da.webm?t=1771435166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714920/extras/2ad563a4674f22e3478f5611dba2c5da.mp4?t=1771435166\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Complete missions to build sauna </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714920/extras/e14a703cfc046f0368851f10632e2926.poster.avif?t=1771435166\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714920/extras/e14a703cfc046f0368851f10632e2926.webm?t=1771435166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714920/extras/e14a703cfc046f0368851f10632e2926.mp4?t=1771435166\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Complete various tasks to unlock items</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714920/extras/1dc7b048c07ce9c20571e0b21374b6c4.avif?t=1771435166\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714920/extras_big/1dc7b048c07ce9c20571e0b21374b6c4.avif?t=1771435166 width=800 height=450 /></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Get behind the wheel of various vehicles: from ATVs to old Soviet trucks</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714920/extras/903f3f3daa5e613305940b5b2e44c089.avif?t=1771435166\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714920/extras_big/903f3f3daa5e613305940b5b2e44c089.avif?t=1771435166 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Build a secluded summer-house with a sauna on an island in the middle of Pastor's Lake</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714920/extras/662d0dba4672403e5f2bba657f072888.avif?t=1771435166\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714920/extras_big/662d0dba4672403e5f2bba657f072888.avif?t=1771435166 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><u>Early Access Roadmap</u></strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_strike\"><i>Fishing with the option to sell or cook your catch</i></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_strike\"><i>Story-based quest about church restoration</i></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_strike\"><i>Sowing, harvesting, and selling wheat</i></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_strike\"><i>Transportation work - taxi, bus driver</i></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_strike\"><i>Leaderboards for game points, fish size, and crayfish catch</i></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_strike\"><i>Urban location (city Sosnovy Bor)</i></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_strike\"><i>Growing and harvesting tomatoes in the garden, maintaining a chicken coop</i></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_strike\"><i>Harvesting and bottling honey from the hive into containers</i></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_strike\">Hunting game with firearms and then selling the catch</span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tasks to restore everyday life in local villages, with an increasing number of NPCs as you progress</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crafting household items, food, and accessories</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customization of country house decor</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expanded quests for finding valuable items on the map</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expansion of the urban location with the introduction of new quests for earning in-game currency</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reworking the visual style of existing locations with an increase in Detailing</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Final fixes and improvements (to locations and game mechanics) before release</u></strong></p></li></ul>",
